{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_04_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら 2話 曲に込めた想い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MVのアイデアを話し合ってから、数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡA few days later after mv meeting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1800,
          "startTime": 1.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、今日は仕事で\nMVの製作会議に行けなくてすみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your hard work. I'm sorry I couldn't attend\nthe MV production meeting today due to work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "私の考えたアイデアはどうでしたか？\n提案は通りましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How do you feel about the idea I came up with?\nWas the proposal accepted?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それなんだが……\nさくらと一緒に考えた案は全部ボツになったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what I wanted to talk about…\nThe ideas Sakura and I came up with were all rejected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "感触は悪くなかったんだが\nもう少し検討した方が良さそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't think it was bad‚\nbut they felt it needed further consideration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……。一生懸命考えたんですけど\n私の力が足りなくてすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… I put a lot of effort into thinking about it‚\nbut I'm sorry my skills weren't enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "本当は私も何か足りない気がしてたんです\n今度の曲は今までのサニピの集大成だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ I also felt like something was lacking.\nThis song is a culmination of Sunny Peace's journey so far…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "曲に込めた想いが伝わるMVにしたいのに\nうまく伝えられる手段が思いつかなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to create an MV that conveys the emotions in the song‚\nbut I can't think of a good way to do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（慣れない作業でさくらも行き詰まっているようだな）\n（もっといいアイデアは何かないか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It seems that Sakura is also struggling to come up with ideas because this is an unfamiliar task.）\n（Is there a better idea…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの集大成か……そうだ\nさくら、明日の仕事の後で俺に付き合ってくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A culmination of Sunny Peace's journey… That's right.\nSakura‚ when your schedule ends tomorrow‚ let's go somewhere for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "いいですけど、どこに行くんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds good‚ but where should we go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのこれまでの軌跡を感じられる場所だ\nそこに行けばMVのヒントが掴めるかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Somewhere that can make you feel Sunny Peace's journey so far.\nYou might find hints for the MV there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡThe next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1133.3333333000014,
          "startTime": 78.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "ここは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This place…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "懐かしいだろ？\nさくらはこの場所を覚えてるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while‚ hasn't it?\nSakura‚ do you remember this place?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　もちろん覚えてます！\nここはサニピが東京で初めてライブをした場所です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ of course‚ I remember!\nThis is where Sunny Peace performed their first live in Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃はまだ東京に慣れてないし……\n初めてのライブで凄く緊張したんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I wasn't familiar with Tokyo at all…\nand it was our first live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんが来てくれるか不安で\n舞台袖からこっそり客席を覗き見たりして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was so anxious‚ wondering what would happen\nif the audience didn't show up‚ so I even peeked out from behind the stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "ここが私達のファンで一杯になるように頑張ろうって\n楽屋でみんなと話したりしたなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remember talking with everyone in the dressing room‚\nsaying that we should work hard to fill this place with our fans. …",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "……こうして見ると記憶よりも小さく感じますね\nステージと客席の距離ってこんなに近かったんだなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking at it now‚ it feels even smaller than I remembered.\nThe distance between the stage and the seats is this close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "最近は大きなステージで歌うことが増えたから\n余計にそう思うのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Recently‚ we've had more opportunities to perform on larger stages‚\nso it might feel even more so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれませんね。ここに来ると\nデビューしたての頃の気持ちを思い出しちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Probably. When I come here‚\nit makes me remember how I felt when we debuted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "ここは駆け出しの新人だったサニピを\n育ててくれた場所です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This place is where Sunny Peace‚\njust rookies at the time‚ were nurtured.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "初心を思い出せたところで次の場所に行こうか\nここがサニピの過去なら、次はサニピの現在だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've reminisced about our beginnings‚ so shall we go to the next place?\nThis place represents Sunny Peace's past‚ and the next one will be Sunny Peace's present.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.1119458321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5388.054167900009,
          "startTime": 151.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.2666666667
