      "text": "大歓声と会場を埋め尽くすサイリウムの光……\nファンのみんなの声援が心強くて勇気づけられました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thunderous cheers and the sea of glowsticks filling the arena…\nthe support from all the fans gave me strength and courage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "小さなライブハウスで歌っていたサニピが\nこの広い会場をファンで埋め尽くすほどになったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace‚ who used to sing in small live houses‚\nhas now grown to the point where we can fill this large venue with fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 332.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 335.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_02-skr031.m4a",
      "text": "……私はアイドルとして成長出来ているんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Am I really growing as an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
